<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #000000; /* Cream background */
            color: #ffffff; /* Dark text */
        }
        .container {
            margin-top: 100px;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #000; /* Black background for the message box */
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .btn-home {
            background-color: #f5f5dc; /* Cream button */
            color: #000; /* Black text */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container text-center text-white">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Password Changed Successfully</h1>
        <p>Your password has been changed successfully!</p>
        <p>For your security, we recommend that you log out and log back in with your new password.</p>
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-home">Go to Login</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
